headline: Cboe Appoints Prashant Bhatia to Lead Enterprise Strategy & Corporate Development
summary: Cboe Global Markets, Inc. (Cboe: CBOE), the world's leading derivatives and securities exchange network, today announced it has appointed Prashant Bhatia as Executive Vice President, Head of Enterprise Strategy & Corporate Development, effective September 2, 2025.
